    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リッド</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reid</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいと思わない？
ファラトスクの騎士！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aren't they awesome?
Those Farahtosk Knights!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>I'm punning here on purpose, but I don't know if that's the intention. Could go with Faratosk or Pharatosk.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだよ、ファラトスクって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heck is a Farahtosk...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ラタトスクの騎士のエミルを倒せば
ファラトスクの騎士の
資格も手に入ると思わない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I can beat Emil, the knight of Ratatosk,
do you think I'll be qualified to become
a Farahtosk Knight?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だからなんだよ、ファラトスクって！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So like I said, what the heck is a Farahtosk Knight?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>よーし、いこう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alriiight, here I go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
